: null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015664, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O He Who has shown only goodness and concealed the evil (deeds of His servants)! O He Who has not censured for the offenses and has not exposed the hidden! O He Who is Ample in pardoning! O He Who is Excellent in overlooking! O He Who is Liberal in forgiveness! O He Who opens His Hands wide with mercy! O He Who is present in all confidential talks! O He Who is the ultimate objective of all complaints! O He Who raises from falls! O He Who is Generous in condonation! O He Who is Great in conferring bounties! O He Who takes the initiative in favoring before they are deserved! O my Lord, O my Lord, O my Lord!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Woh jisne achhaai ko zaahir kiya aur buraai ko chhipaayaa! Ay Woh jo gunah par giraft nahi karta aur pardah faash nahi karta! Ay bohot maaf karne waale, ay beh-tareen dar-guzar karne waale, ay wasee bakhshish waale, ay khule haath rahmat karne waale, ay har raaz ke jaanne waale aur har shikaayat khatm karne waale, ay khataae’n maaf karne waale, ay dar-guzar aur maaf karne waale kareem, ay bohot ehsaan karne waale, ay haq-daar hone se pehle ne’mate’n a’taa farma ne waale, ay Paalne waale, ay Paalne waale, ay Paalne waale.", "Urdu": "اے وہ جس نے اچھائی کو ظاہر کیا اوربرائی کو چھپایا!اے وہ جو گناہ پر گرفت نہیں کرتا اور پردہ فاش نہیں کرتا اے بہت معاف کرنے والے اے بہترین درگزر کرنے والے اے وسیع بخشش والے اے کھلے ہاتھوں رحمت کرنے والے اے ہر راز کے جاننے والے اور ہر شکایت ختم کرنے والے اے خطائیں معاف کرنے والے اے درگزراورمعاف کرنے والے کریم اے بہت احسان کرنے والے اے حق دارہونے سے پہلے نعمتیں عطا فرمانے والے۔ اے پالنے والے۔اے پالنے والے۔ اے پالنے والے۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAN AZ-HARAL JAMEELA, WA SATA-RAL QABEE-HA, YAA MAN LAM YOAA-KHIZ BIL-JAREE-RATE, WA LAM YAH-TEKAS SITRA, YAA AZEE-MAL A’FEW, YAA HASANAT TAJAA-WUZE, YAA WAASE-A’L MAGH-FERATE, YAA BAASE-TAL YA-DAIY-NE BIR-RAHMATE, YAA SAAHEBA KULLE NAJWAA, WA MUNTA-HAA KULLE SHAK-WAA, YAA MOQEE-LAL A’SA-RAATE, YAA KAREE-MAS SAFHE, YAA A’ZEE-MAL MANNE, YAA MUB-TADE-AN BIN-NE-A’ME QABLAS TE-QAAQE-HAA, YAA RABBAAHO, YAA RABBAAHO, YAA RABBAAHO.", "ArabicText1": "يَا مَنْ اَظْهَرَ الْجَمِيْلَ؛ وَسَتَرَ الْقَبِيْحَ؛ يَا مَنْ لَمْ يُؤَاخِذْ بِالْجَرِيْرَةِ؛ وَلَمْ يَهْتِكِ السِّتْرَ؛ يَا عَظِيْمَ الْعَفْوِ؛ يَا حَسَنَ التَّجَاوُزِ؛ يَا وَاسِعَ الْمَغْفِرَةِ؛ يَا بَاسِطَ الْيَدَيْنِ بِالرَّحْمَةِ؛ يَا صَاحِبَ كُلِّ نَجْوٰى؛ وَمُنْتَهٰى كُلِّ شَكْوٰى؛ يَا مُقِيْلَ الْعَثَرَاتِ؛ يَا كَرِيْمَ الصَّفْحِ؛ يَا عَظِيْمَ الْمَنِّ؛ يَا مُبْتَدِئًا بِالنِّعَمِ قَبْلَ اسْتِحْقَاقِهَا؛ يَا رَبَّاهُ يَا رَبَّاهُ يَا رَبَّاهُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": nul